<P>
MAIL DELIVERY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I can certainly validate that the mail is getting slower and slower (June 
29).On June 23 I received a letter from Gov. Pete Wilson that had been written 
and was postmarked June 10 in Sacramento. Apparently even the governor's mail 
cannot be delivered in a timely manner. 
</P>
<P>
 Bring back the pony express! They could have carried a letter from Sacramento 
to Los Angeles in less than 13 days. 
</P>
<P>
 JOYCE K. BROSEY 
</P>
