everything is happening in about nine languages at once.The translations are 
stilted, or frequently merely stupid. But the award for the worst goes to the 
Bulgarian translator phrasing an answer by Coach Dimitar Penev about how soon 
his team will begin preparing for its semifinal against Italy. 
