</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KATHLEEN DOHENY 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Summer colds can feel twice as miserable as winter ones. Options and fees for 
relief and comfort: 
</P>
<P>
 * Vitamin C Pop (lollipop with 65 milligrams of vitamin C), 39 cents. 
</P>
<P>
