 The City Council has appointed three people to the Planning Commission and 
four to the Parks and Recreation Commission. 
</P>
<P>
 Named to the Planning Commission were Marge Kasalek, Nanette Lunn and Howard 
Mitzman.Their two-year terms will begin July 25, according to Tustin Chief 
Deputy Clerk Valerie Whiteman. 
</P>
<P>
 Kasalek, who has served on the Planning Commission for the past four years, is 
a small-business co-owner who previously worked as a purchasing agent for a 
