the cities of Tustin and Walnut Creek. Cormack, who was named to his second 
term on the commission, is a clinical research associate. Hillyard is a former 
senior manager with Martinez-based Discovery Toys. Jackson is a word processor 
and regional office news reporter for State Farm Insurance in Irvine. 
