<TEXT>
<P>
 Wrong building -- A photo caption in World Report on June 21 misidentified a 
building at the Sikh religious complex in Amritsar, India. The building shown 
is the Hari Mandir, or Temple of God. It is commonly called the Golden Temple. 
</P>
