<TEXT>
<P>
 Water Quote -- A story published in Saturday's Times incorrectly quoted the 
Rev. Darrel Meyers, a Van Nuys pastor who recently toured the Middle East. The 
correct quote is, "The average Israeli settler consumes 27 times the amount of 
water that Palestinians use." Meyers also stated that an Israeli foreign 
minister told him half the water in the Gaza Strip is wasted. 
</P>
